    WorkshopEntitiesResourceAssemblerAbstract<T extends WorkshopEntity>
    To construct custom navigable Links for a given Resource and its subResources (e.g. to get pageable collection of all the Orders modified by Employee through Employee.getOrdersModifiedBy with the ability to iterate them page by page with 'nextPage', 'lastPage' Links etc) you have to use WorkshopEntitiesResourceAssemblerAbstract.toPagedSubResources(Page, Long, String) method by passing the desired ControllerMethodName and only override WorkshopEntitiesResourceAssemblerAbstract.getPagedLink(Pageable, int, String, String, String, String, Long, String) method to implement your custom logic depending on given 'controllerMethodName'.
